The following modifications were made to the source files:

viewer.js
* `TileSource.scannedAt` property added to remove hard-coded value of "40"
* `TileSource.maxZoomLevel` property added to restrict maximum zoom level
* Zoom logic modified to introduce "limit maximum zoom value" behaviour
* New zoom in & zoom out images

"zoomin.svg", "zoomout.svg" images added.

SlideAtlas-viewer original repo: https://github.com/Kitware/SlideAtlas-viewer
SlideAtlas-viewer with enhancements (current version) repo: https://github.com/rodichenko/SlideAtlas-viewer
